    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This beauty is in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. Not a single scratch or hiccup to be found. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this perfection. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
