    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You honestly won't believe your eyes when you see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like an absolute dream, and has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the wait, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
