    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a museum-quality example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. The mechanical state is impeccable, featuring a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline and a lightning-quick M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) that maintains perfect hydraulic pressure. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a pristine subframe and factory-spec dampening that provides telepathic feedback. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the powertrain operates at peak volumetric efficiency. With a flawless underbody and an engine bay free of heat-cycle fatigue, this vehicle offers a pure, visceral driving experience intended for the most demanding collector.",
